      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software used in the analysis must be verified through documented QA procedures including version control, regression testing, and audit trails.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022 R2 is a commercially validated FEA platform with documented QA procedures, version-controlled releases, and regression test suites. Internal DePuy Synthes SOPs governing simulation software qualification were followed. Achieved level exceeds required level."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
